metadata.name: Diamond #1/42
metadata.description:
I used to hate my shadow self, the parts of me that I kept hidden and wanted to change. 
But through my journey, I've learned that my shadow is not something to be suppressed. Instead, I've discovered the immense potential and strength it holds.  
Now, I embrace it and use it to co-create. By unifying both polarities, a sense of grace is born.  
Accepting both my flaws and virtues creates a diamond with thousands of nuances, giving me a broader perception of the world.

This mural was created through a partnership with @adistrictmx 

Check out the memories of the mural here:

https://tinyurl.com/2j2jsgek
